import logo from './logo.svg'; import './App.css'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import Title from './Title.js'; function App() { return (
<header className="App-header"> <img src={logo} className="App-logo" alt="logo" /> <p> Bear Blog </p> <div class = "button" style = "inline-block"> <Link to="/"> <button className = "app_bottomButtonleft"> Home </button> </Link> <Link to="/profile"> <button className = "app_bottomButtonright"> Profile </button> </Link> </div> <a className="App-link" href="https://reactjs.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" > Learn React </a> </header> </div> ); } export default App;
